  </div></li>
  <li><span class="check-box" data-key="do-4b">✓</span><div><strong>Watch: Appliance panels</strong><br><span class="do-muted">Learn how to spec appliance panels — the decorative panels that surround refrigerators, dishwashers, and other exposed appliances to match your cabinetry.</span>
    <div class="video-embed">
      <video controls preload="metadata" playsinline>
        <source src="/videos/appliance-panels.mp4" type="video/mp4" />
